<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="BeanMind Curator support page" />
  <title>BeanMind Curator Support</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --blue: #2d9cff;
      --text: #111827;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --line: #e5e7eb;
      --bg: #ffffff;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
        "Noto Sans KR", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .hero {
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
    }

    .hero img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    main {
      width: min(760px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 56px auto 80px;
    }

    .support-title {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 42px);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      font-size: 26px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .card p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }

    .label {
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    a {
      color: var(--blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 28px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      main {
        margin-top: 40px;
      }

      .card h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .card p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <header class="hero">
    <img src="Hero-01.png" alt="BeanMind Curator Hero Banner" />
  </header>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <main>
    <h1 class="support-title">BeanMind Support</h1>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>BeanMind Curator에 오신걸 환영합니다.</h2>

      <p>
        BeanMind는 AI 기반 커피 추천 및 큐레이션 서비스입니다.
      </p>

      <p>
        서비스 이용 중 문의사항이나 오류 제보는 아래 이메일로 연락해주세요.
      </p>

      <p class="label">문의 이메일</p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:wkjeon@gmail.com">wkjeon@gmail.com</a>
      </p>

      <p class="label">운영 시간</p>
      <p>평일 10:00 ~ 18:00 (KST)</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    © 2026 BeanMind. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
